    "Thus, this section focuses on the capabilities of the algorithms available in the packages listed in Table 7, which tend to be well-maintained and documented.",
    "In our view, there is little consensus in the literature on what might be the best algorithm in any particular context, so the focus here is on providing some guidelines to choosing and using algorithms, rather than attempting to provide a definitive guide.",
